@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lllmmw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(0.91)
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.15) * (tmp + 0.15 / tmp + 0.38)) - (v1 + v1))
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.71)) + wp.cos((v0 + 0.97 + v2 + 0.63)))
    data[tid] = v0
